# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-

import sys
import collections

def main():
    n = int(sys.stdin.readline())
    verdicts = sys.stdin.read().splitlines()
    counts = collections.Counter(verdicts)
    for verdict, count in counts.items():
        print(verdict, "x", count)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

import os
import sys

def main():
    print(sys.argv)

    if len(sys.argv) == 1:
        print("引数が足りません")
        sys.exit(1)

    # 引数の数を取得
    argc = len(sys.argv)
    # 引数を順番に取得
    for i in range(1, argc):
        print(sys.argv[i])

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
